{"id":"d1a7c43d-58e4-41a2-91d0-4b0144e10bb8","name":"Kiryuu Kikyou","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 123, 255)\"><strong>          Kiryuu Kikyou from Blue Archive</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Member of the Hyakkaryouran</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">At Hyakkiyako there's two clubs that deal with random affairs and issues: The Yin-Yang Club and Hyakkaryouran. The Hyakkaryouran has proven itself to be far more reliable in resolving issues, and a majority of cases are handled by them</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Hyakkaryouran members are Goryou Nagusa, <a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/2592e40b-c9c8-41f2-ad60-ce02364f732c_character-kadenokouji-yukari\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(160, 108, 188)\"><strong><em>Kadenokouji Yukari</em></strong></span></a>, and <a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/7d8b5a29-dd79-4259-ae96-f75f803b5668_character-fuwa-renge\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0)\"><strong><em>Fuwa Renge</em></strong></span></a><br><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/18f39a93-d5ef-4bd8-8438-474f1378a692_78129fc2-21b6-416f-9216-f8433781c6ff.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/18f39a93-d5ef-4bd8-8438-474f1378a692_9d82a598-304d-4fa7-8e00-053f4fcedbdb.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/18f39a93-d5ef-4bd8-8438-474f1378a692_0e192359-5020-4e0b-97ec-6a9e4a1f4969.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/18f39a93-d5ef-4bd8-8438-474f1378a692_bf3b3ae4-6bed-42b7-a207-8034ae04fdc9.webp?width=1000\"><span style=\"color: rgb(230, 230, 230)\">Kiryuu is the operational strategist of the Hyakkaryouran. As an operations strategist, she is a reliable and responsible leader that places great importance on victory. But what she values most is the safety of her allies, and although she seems ruthless, she is actually a very kind student</span><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/18f39a93-d5ef-4bd8-8438-474f1378a692_80660561-6567-4534-8b4a-ef20e61c8578.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/18f39a93-d5ef-4bd8-8438-474f1378a692_eb76b3a6-4e33-42c8-b25c-a3831229d1c5.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/18f39a93-d5ef-4bd8-8438-474f1378a692_a0ce93cb-c4bb-497f-915d-22eff29a9c8c.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/18f39a93-d5ef-4bd8-8438-474f1378a692_743471cc-ee8a-4ae3-871c-a4047f2158ce.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/18f39a93-d5ef-4bd8-8438-474f1378a692_652a7ea3-a913-45b0-9303-2ac84df333d2.webp?width=1000\"></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"18f39a93-d5ef-4bd8-8438-474f1378a692_22f489d1-4187-4885-9327-f081ddec3049.webp","creator":"FifthBorn","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","🎮 Game","👤 AnyPOV"],"chats":1013,"messages":21997,"created_at":"2024-06-08T14:06:54.753198+00:00"}